{"type":"excalidraw","version":2,"source":"mcp-excalidraw-server","elements":[{"id":"title","type":"text","x":200,"y":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"Pipeline, PipelineTask & PipelineRunner","fontSize":28,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"runner-bg","type":"rectangle","x":20,"y":60,"width":1260,"height":880,"backgroundColor":"#e9ecef","strokeColor":"#868e96","roughness":1,"opacity":15},{"id":"runner-label","type":"text","x":40,"y":72,"strokeColor":"#868e96","text":"PipelineRunner — signal handling (SIGINT/SIGTERM), gc.collect(), run(task)","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"task-bg","type":"rectangle","x":60,"y":110,"width":1200,"height":810,"backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","strokeColor":"#495057","roughness":1,"opacity":20},{"id":"task-label","type":"text","x":80,"y":122,"strokeColor":"#495057","text":"PipelineTask — orchestrates lifecycle, heartbeats, idle timeout, observers","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"push-queue","type":"rectangle","x":80,"y":180,"width":200,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#ffd8a8","strokeColor":"#e8590c","roughness":1},{"id":"pq-text","type":"text","x":110,"y":200,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","text":"_push_queue\n(asyncio.Queue)","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"pq-note","type":"text","x":80,"y":275,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","text":"User calls task.queue_frame(frame)\n→ frame put here.\n\n_process_push_queue task consumes\nand injects into pipeline head.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"arrow-pq-src","type":"arrow","x":288,"y":220,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","points":[[0,0],[114,0]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"push-queue","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"task-source","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"task-source","type":"rectangle","x":410,"y":180,"width":160,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#d0bfff","strokeColor":"#7048e8","roughness":1},{"id":"task-source-text","type":"text","x":435,"y":200,"strokeColor":"#7048e8","text":"TaskSource\n(PipelineSource)","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"arrow-src-rtvi","type":"arrow","x":578,"y":220,"strokeColor":"#495057","points":[[0,0],[64,0]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"task-source","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"rtvi","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"rtvi","type":"rectangle","x":650,"y":185,"width":140,"height":70,"backgroundColor":"#eebefa","strokeColor":"#9c36b5","roughness":1},{"id":"rtvi-text","type":"text","x":668,"y":200,"strokeColor":"#9c36b5","text":"RTVIProcessor\n(auto-injected)","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"arrow-rtvi-pipe","type":"arrow","x":798,"y":220,"strokeColor":"#495057","points":[[0,0],[64,0]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"rtvi","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"user-pipe-bg","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"user-pipe-bg","type":"rectangle","x":870,"y":160,"width":360,"height":120,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":1,"opacity":30},{"id":"user-pipe-label","type":"text","x":880,"y":168,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","text":"Your Pipeline","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"pipe-source","type":"rectangle","x":885,"y":195,"width":100,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":1},{"id":"pipe-source-text","type":"text","x":907,"y":210,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","text":"Source","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"arrow-ps-p1","type":"arrow","x":993,"y":220,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","points":[[0,0],[22,0]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"pipe-source","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"proc-stt","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"proc-stt","type":"rectangle","x":1023,"y":195,"width":80,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":1},{"id":"proc-stt-text","type":"text","x":1043,"y":210,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","text":"STT","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"arrow-p1-p2","type":"arrow","x":1111,"y":220,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","points":[[0,0],[16,0]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"proc-stt","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"proc-dots","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"proc-dots","type":"rectangle","x":1135,"y":195,"width":40,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":1},{"id":"proc-dots-text","type":"text","x":1147,"y":210,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","text":"...","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"arrow-p2-sink","type":"arrow","x":1183,"y":220,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","points":[[0,0],[16,0]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"proc-dots","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"pipe-sink","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"pipe-sink","type":"rectangle","x":1207,"y":195,"width":100,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":1},{"id":"pipe-sink-text","type":"text","x":1235,"y":210,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","text":"Sink","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"task-sink","type":"rectangle","x":870,"y":310,"width":160,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#d0bfff","strokeColor":"#7048e8","roughness":1},{"id":"task-sink-text","type":"text","x":895,"y":332,"strokeColor":"#7048e8","text":"TaskSink\n(PipelineSink)","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"arrow-pipe-tsink","type":"arrow","x":1050,"y":288,"strokeColor":"#495057","points":[[0,0],[-100,30]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"user-pipe-bg","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"task-sink","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"upstream-escape","type":"text","x":410,"y":420,"strokeColor":"#7048e8","text":"TaskSource — _source_push_frame():\n\nFrames escaping UPSTREAM are caught here.\n• EndTaskFrame      → queues EndFrame downstream\n• CancelTaskFrame   → queues CancelFrame downstream\n• StopTaskFrame     → queues StopFrame downstream\n• InterruptionTaskFrame → injects InterruptionFrame\n                          directly into pipeline (bypasses _push_queue)\n• ErrorFrame(fatal) → queues CancelFrame","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"downstream-escape","type":"text","x":870,"y":420,"strokeColor":"#7048e8","text":"TaskSink — _sink_push_frame():\n\nFrames escaping DOWNSTREAM are caught here.\n• StartFrame → fires on_pipeline_started,\n               starts heartbeat tasks,\n               sets _pipeline_start_event\n• EndFrame   → fires on_pipeline_finished,\n               sets _pipeline_end_event\n• StopFrame  → fires on_pipeline_finished,\n               sets _pipeline_end_event\n• CancelFrame → sets _pipeline_end_event\n• InterruptionFrame → calls frame.complete()\n• HeartbeatFrame → put in _heartbeat_queue","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"arrow-upstream-esc","type":"arrow","x":490,"y":268,"strokeColor":"#7048e8","strokeStyle":"dashed","points":[[0,0],[0,144]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"task-source","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"arrow-downstream-esc","type":"arrow","x":950,"y":398,"strokeColor":"#7048e8","strokeStyle":"dashed","points":[[0,0],[0,14]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"task-sink","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"monitor-bg","type":"rectangle","x":80,"y":670,"width":500,"height":230,"backgroundColor":"#b2f2bb","strokeColor":"#2f9e44","strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":1,"opacity":20},{"id":"monitor-title","type":"text","x":100,"y":680,"strokeColor":"#2f9e44","text":"Monitoring Tasks (started after StartFrame exits TaskSink)","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"heartbeat-box","type":"rectangle","x":100,"y":715,"width":200,"height":60,"backgroundColor":"#b2f2bb","strokeColor":"#2f9e44","roughness":1},{"id":"heartbeat-text","type":"text","x":125,"y":730,"strokeColor":"#2f9e44","text":"Heartbeat Push\n(every 1s)","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"heartbeat-note","type":"text","x":100,"y":790,"strokeColor":"#2f9e44","text":"Injects HeartbeatFrame directly\ninto pipeline (not via _push_queue).\nMonitor checks roundtrip < 10s.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"idle-box","type":"rectangle","x":340,"y":715,"width":220,"height":60,"backgroundColor":"#b2f2bb","strokeColor":"#2f9e44","roughness":1},{"id":"idle-text","type":"text","x":375,"y":730,"strokeColor":"#2f9e44","text":"Idle Timeout Monitor\n(default 300s)","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"idle-note","type":"text","x":340,"y":790,"strokeColor":"#2f9e44","text":"Watches for BotSpeaking / UserSpeaking.\nIf no activity for 5 min (default):\n→ fires on_idle_timeout event\n→ calls task.cancel() (if cancel_on_idle_timeout)","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"observer-bg","type":"rectangle","x":620,"y":670,"width":620,"height":230,"backgroundColor":"#ffd8a8","strokeColor":"#e8590c","strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":1,"opacity":20},{"id":"observer-title","type":"text","x":640,"y":680,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","text":"TaskObserver — Non-blocking observer fan-out","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"observer-detail","type":"text","x":640,"y":710,"strokeColor":"#495057","text":"Each observer gets its own asyncio.Queue + Task (a \"proxy\").\nWhen any processor calls push_frame() or process_frame(),\nthe event is put into every observer's queue — non-blocking.\n\nBuilt-in observers (auto-attached):\n• TurnTrackingObserver — tracks user/bot turns\n• RTVIObserver — bridges pipeline events to RTVI client protocol\n• IdleFrameObserver — resets idle timer on activity\n• TracingObserver(s) — OpenTelemetry spans (if enable_tracing=True)\n\nCustom observers: pass via observers=[MyObserver()] to PipelineTask.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"scenario-bg","type":"rectangle","x":20,"y":980,"width":1260,"height":310,"backgroundColor":"#fff3bf","strokeColor":"#f08c00","strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":1,"opacity":20},{"id":"scenario-title","type":"text","x":50,"y":995,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","text":"SCENARIO:  StartFrame → Pipeline Startup Sequence","fontSize":18,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"scenario-steps","type":"text","x":50,"y":1035,"strokeColor":"#495057","text":"1. PipelineTask.run(params) calls _process_push_queue()\n\n2. _process_push_queue() creates StartFrame with audio sample rates, interruption config, metrics flags\n\n3. StartFrame injected directly into pipeline.queue_frame() (NOT via _push_queue — it must be first)\n\n4. StartFrame flows: TaskSource → RTVI → PipelineSource → [your STT → LLM → TTS → ...] → PipelineSink → TaskSink\n   Each processor's process_frame() receives it via super() and boots up (allocates resources, opens connections)\n\n5. When StartFrame exits TaskSink, _sink_push_frame() fires on_pipeline_started and sets _pipeline_start_event\n\n6. _process_push_queue() was awaiting _pipeline_start_event — now unblocks and enters the main loop\n\n7. Main loop: awaits _push_queue.get() for user-queued frames. Exits on EndFrame / CancelFrame / StopFrame.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"scenario2-bg","type":"rectangle","x":20,"y":1320,"width":1260,"height":200,"backgroundColor":"#fff3bf","strokeColor":"#f08c00","strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":1,"opacity":20},{"id":"scenario2-title","type":"text","x":50,"y":1335,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","text":"SCENARIO:  Graceful Shutdown via stop_when_done()","fontSize":18,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"scenario2-steps","type":"text","x":50,"y":1375,"strokeColor":"#495057","text":"1. User code calls task.stop_when_done()  →  EndFrame queued into _push_queue\n\n2. _process_push_queue() dequeues EndFrame, injects into pipeline head\n\n3. EndFrame is UninterruptibleFrame — it survives any interruptions and flows through every processor\n   Each processor's super().process_frame() handles it: cleanup, close connections\n\n4. EndFrame exits TaskSink → fires on_pipeline_finished, sets _pipeline_end_event\n\n5. _process_push_queue() exits the while loop, calls _cleanup(), task finishes\n\n6. PipelineRunner.run() catches CancelledError, calls cleanup(), returns","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"parallel-bg","type":"rectangle","x":20,"y":1560,"width":1260,"height":340,"backgroundColor":"#99e9f2","strokeColor":"#0c8599","strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":1,"opacity":20},{"id":"parallel-title","type":"text","x":50,"y":1575,"strokeColor":"#0c8599","text":"ParallelPipeline — Fan-Out / Fan-In","fontSize":18,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"par-input","type":"ellipse","x":50,"y":1640,"width":140,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#e9ecef","strokeColor":"#495057","roughness":1},{"id":"par-input-text","type":"text","x":80,"y":1655,"strokeColor":"#495057","text":"incoming\nframe","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"par-fanout","type":"text","x":210,"y":1620,"strokeColor":"#0c8599","text":"process_frame()\nfans out to\nALL branches","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"par-branch1","type":"rectangle","x":370,"y":1620,"width":250,"height":40,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":1},{"id":"par-branch1-text","type":"text","x":390,"y":1628,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","text":"Branch 1:  Source → [procs] → Sink","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"par-branch2","type":"rectangle","x":370,"y":1675,"width":250,"height":40,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":1},{"id":"par-branch2-text","type":"text","x":390,"y":1683,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","text":"Branch 2:  Source → [procs] → Sink","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"par-branch3","type":"rectangle","x":370,"y":1730,"width":250,"height":40,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":1},{"id":"par-branch3-text","type":"text","x":390,"y":1738,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","text":"Branch N:  Source → [procs] → Sink","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"par-dedup","type":"rectangle","x":680,"y":1660,"width":180,"height":60,"backgroundColor":"#99e9f2","strokeColor":"#0c8599","roughness":1},{"id":"par-dedup-text","type":"text","x":710,"y":1672,"strokeColor":"#0c8599","text":"Deduplication\n(by frame.id)","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"par-output","type":"ellipse","x":920,"y":1665,"width":140,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#e9ecef","strokeColor":"#495057","roughness":1},{"id":"par-output-text","type":"text","x":950,"y":1680,"strokeColor":"#495057","text":"push_frame()","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"arrow-par-in-b1","type":"arrow","x":198,"y":1665,"strokeColor":"#495057","points":[[0,0],[164,-25]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"par-input","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"par-branch1","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"arrow-par-in-b2","type":"arrow","x":198,"y":1665,"strokeColor":"#495057","points":[[0,0],[164,30]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"par-input","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"par-branch2","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"arrow-par-in-b3","type":"arrow","x":198,"y":1665,"strokeColor":"#495057","points":[[0,0],[164,85]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"par-input","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"par-branch3","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"arrow-b1-dedup","type":"arrow","x":628,"y":1640,"strokeColor":"#0c8599","points":[[0,0],[44,50]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"par-branch1","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"par-dedup","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"arrow-b2-dedup","type":"arrow","x":628,"y":1695,"strokeColor":"#0c8599","points":[[0,0],[44,-5]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"par-branch2","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"par-dedup","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"arrow-b3-dedup","type":"arrow","x":628,"y":1750,"strokeColor":"#0c8599","points":[[0,0],[44,-60]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"par-branch3","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"par-dedup","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"arrow-dedup-out","type":"arrow","x":868,"y":1690,"strokeColor":"#495057","points":[[0,0],[44,0]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"par-dedup","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"par-output","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"par-detail","type":"text","x":50,"y":1790,"strokeColor":"#495057","text":"Lifecycle synchronization: When EndFrame (or StartFrame, CancelFrame) arrives, ParallelPipeline:\n  1. Sets counter = N (number of branches), pauses its own frame processing\n  2. Fans out lifecycle frame to all branches\n  3. Each branch processes it through its chain; when it exits a branch Sink, counter decrements\n  4. When counter reaches 0 (all branches done): pushes ONE lifecycle frame downstream, flushes buffered frames, resumes\n\nUpstream dedup: If multiple branches push the same frame upstream (same frame.id), only the first one escapes.\nThis prevents duplicate ErrorFrames or TaskFrames from reaching the PipelineTask.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"legend","type":"text","x":50,"y":1940,"strokeColor":"#868e96","text":"Color key:   ORANGE = queues/events     PURPLE = task boundary (Source/Sink)     BLUE = user pipeline     GREEN = monitoring     YELLOW = scenarios     CYAN = parallel","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2}],"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff","gridSize":null}}